<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="article-table" align="left"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#cfcfbb"><tr><td>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="8" bgcolor="#ffffff"><tr><td>
<a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=3&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Huge Event on Quellious</a><br/></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<img src='themes//images/pixel.gif' height='5' width='1' border='0' alt=''/><br/>
</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">This friday, April 19th, at 9:00 PM EST (6 PST) There will be an arena tournament in Freeport on the Quellious server. This event is hosted by Norrath's Defenders. We are essentially a new guild, and dont have many high level members, so we want to find new members and are looking to make a name for ourselves.<br />
<br />
Ok, so what exactly is an arena tournament? Ok, It is a series of fights in the Freeport arena. Small admission fees will be charged, and players will be put into combat with other players of similar levels. The last few players surviving will split up the rewards. The entry fees and divisions are listed below...<br />
<br />
Levels 1-7 Free Entry Norrath's Defenders will supply prizes<br />
Levels 8-15 5pp Entry Fee<br />
Levels 16-23 10pp<br />
Levels 24-33 25pp<br />
Levels 34-43 50pp<br />
Levels 44-49 75pp<br />
Levels 50-60 100pp<br />
<br />
Individual challenges will be allowed, so if you got a grudge against someone, or just have a friend you like to fight with, bring them along. Also there will be group competitions allowed.<br />
<br />
I have contacted several of Quellious's GMs and many of them said they would like to drop by, so there is a good chance there will be GMs at this event. I am also going to invite some of the major guilds on Quellious, So this event might be HUGE.<br />
<br />
Also, at this event, there will be gambling on each of the fights assuming we can find a rich person willing to sponsor it. There will be door prizes too for anyone that has registered to fight. Between fights there will be time for auctions, so if you have some gear you need to sell bring it with you.<br />
<br />
So lets review, for the entry fee of your level, you get...<br />
- Entry into several arena fights with potential to make a fortune.<br />
- Door Prizes<br />
- Lots of Beer<br />
- Gambling<br />
<br />
Ok, well I hope to see you there, if you are interested in attending, send an email to NorrathsDefender&#115;&#064;&#104;otmail.com with ENTRY as the subject. Please give your characters name, level, and class.<br />
<br />
If you have a lot of money (and are an honest individual) we may be interested in having you support the gambling at the arena. If you are interested in sponsoring Gambling, send me an email to NorrathsDefender&#115;&#064;&#104;otmail.com with the subject GAMBLING, please include character info.<br />
<br />
Finally if you would like to donate door prizes, it would be great publicity, just see it now... &quot;(A Grateful Newbie) has just won (A Valuable Item) compliments of (A generous person/guild)&quot; so if you would like to donate a door prize, send me an email at NorrathsDefender&#115;&#064;&#104;otmail.com with the subject DOOR PRIZE. It is a great way to make people look kindly on your guild.<br />
<br />
Well I will have complete rules available on request to those who as for them, and anyone that registers, you dont have to pay the entry fee until the event. Send an email with the subject INFO for more information. And just so you know, evil races are welcome too, invisibility will be provided to anyone who needs it to make it to the arena.<br />
<br />
Im sure I have forgot something, so look for more of my messages through out this page. So Have fun, hope to see you there, and Bring your friends.<br />
<br />
See you on Quellious<br />
Kasmire- Norrath's Defenders<br />
<br />
NOTE* This was originally posted on everlore.com and you can check there for updates. I really hope Lotus Cult can be a part of this grand event, it will even give you a chance to prove you are the BEST.<br /><br /></td></tr></table><br/>
